sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as Payment Screen
    participant Pay as Payment Service
    participant API as API Controller
    participant QR as VietQR Service
    participant DB as Database

    U->>UI: Click "Thanh Toán"
    UI->>U: Show Total Amount
    U->>UI: Select Method "Chuyển khoản QR"
    
    UI->>Pay: GetSettingsAsync()
    Pay->>API: GET /api/PaymentSettings
    API-->>Pay: Return Bank Info (VCB, AccNo)
    
    Pay->>QR: Generate QR Link (Amount, Content)
    QR-->>UI: Return QR Image URL
    UI->>U: Display QR & Wait
    
    U->>UI: Confirm "Khách đã chuyển"
    UI->>Pay: CompleteOrderAsync(OrderId, Amount)
    Pay->>API: PUT /api/Orders/{id}/Complete
    
    API->>DB: Update Order.Status = Completed
    API->>DB: Insert Payment Record
    API->>DB: Update Table.Status = Available
    
    API-->>Pay: Success
    Pay-->>UI: Close Dialog
    UI->>U: Print Receipt (Optional)
